{"tid":309112,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"每月一次board game 巴絲打聚會 (第五次聚會招募)","createTime":"2017-07-04T17:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T08:32:02.000Z","uid":62225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"914c24e3467baf35672fa3ea337ae86bea67808a","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"黎緊會係第五次聚會<br />\n<br />\n我地主要以一齊玩Board Game 為主 (多數玩一d 可以大家一齊笑既game，有時用小小腦既game，次次唔同。例如，牛頭王，矮人掘金等，仲會有好多好多類型既）<br />\n多數每次都會有d 新遊戲同新朋友，所以一定會教大家玩同埋有d 小遊戲比大家認識一下先。<br />\n<br />\n試過去board game cafe，但而家鍾意book活動室玩，多d 私人空間無咁嘈。<br />\n<br />\n暫時人數唔算好多，想加入多d 巴絲。現時年齡18-22，target 有12人以上既pool。<br />\n我地都係一班平時無fd子，放假放學放工無乜朋友所以好悶，大毒小毒既人，單拖同有朋友一齊黎都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我地都係較為靜同內向，唔係太識social，所以board game 幾岩我地互動。<br />\n同埋board game 可以有d 目標咁同人有多d 交流，好岩內向既你，慢慢都會訓練到自己。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就留低contact。第五次聚會會係黎緊星期五晚 (7/7)，book左個活動室會準備3個board game 比大家玩。<br />\nDetail 及報名link<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePvo37Fw22bx6wczAr8O7ZF5Lif6Wwvq_e94w3wm_OpimxFQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSePvo37Fw22bx6wczAr8O7ZF5Lif6Wwvq_e94w3wm_OpimxFQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=TifsVXGEX01NjSRDsVQgDPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=232f5672\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePvo37Fw22bx6wczAr8O7ZF5Lif6Wwvq_e94w3wm_OpimxFQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n上次第四次都已經招到十幾廿個contact，但係可能大家就唔到時間，所以上次我地有9人。<br />\n黎唔到今次聚會可以留左contact先，方便之後加入。"},{"pid":"161e1d3fee1128456910cbb2e7cbf78c9676a70f","tid":309112,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"有冇扑game?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e55be9c6a50fb1201ca89ff45c21b8d9842c04a","tid":309112,"uid":25902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"黃大仙好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd2a9acfe35d3f60ff3f0d97f72e99d016c76c9","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃大仙好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔算呀 其實都ok 方便"},{"pid":"e9790e36f26182fb66914a76cf51b957a6dda85c","tid":309112,"uid":52525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"Fd子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 7/7要睇小隊長大結局 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dce2404d5d208183b58802e2536d9e9bfa242a3","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fd子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 7/7要睇小隊長大結局 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7276f5c7f6e1709196fae3b951e3d5ec0687f2cb","tid":309112,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"呢個月玩咩？"},{"pid":"3f56a8091a06c30f788a8ec4de01af4f76e95b45","tid":309112,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:40:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca6f63c5577d6b4cc5eb0b4020e02047663cea55","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個月玩咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今月主題 鬥智鬥力"},{"pid":"a954d39d0e78f8c1a85295c2ea59270aafff4ba9","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大過22<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都welcome ga"},{"pid":"1ada187104105cd8ebda8f77cc9920cb4981452a","tid":309112,"uid":688