quote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得我識樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你識既樓主係個點既人</blockquote><br />\n住龍乜樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但要識我應該真係唔難既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相認失敗"},{"pid":"275d8fd72baed73bd2cc2011d70ff436d74c7044","tid":309112,"uid":36491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"聽晚得閒，想知有咩玩？<br />\n洗唔洗我帶D board game黎？"},{"pid":"3fc0160859b1f72b47439cdaa5f511ca9c2e9710","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得我識樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你識既樓主係個點既人</blockquote><br />\n住龍乜樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但要識我應該真係唔難既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相認失敗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家你咪識左我law"},{"pid":"83e97611a0047496434a7ac7843d969787441190","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽晚得閒，想知有咩玩？<br />\n洗唔洗我帶D board game黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地好多都係新手，巴打你會有咩介紹？？"},{"pid":"6285535c10cb463199a0d6f25e531470e3e2d52e","tid":309112,"uid":36491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽晚得閒，想知有咩玩？<br />\n洗唔洗我帶D board game黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地好多都係新手，巴打你會有咩介紹？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時我都會買/帶D 新board game同我d fd玩，試過以下幾隻都OK易上手<br />\n<br />\n1)<br />\nBang The Dice Game<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/153550_ed143da556835022bf9220d523aacde8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F153550_ed143da556835022bf9220d523aacde8.jpg&h=a406a16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三國殺初原&quot;Bang&quot;既變化版，<br />\n用骰仔玩，變相隻一次都好靠運氣，所以更加容上手<br />\n<br />\n2) 香料之路<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/154032_ed32cbb9ca71ce300768f88acbd8f348.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F154032_ed32cbb9ca71ce300768f88acbd8f348.png&h=1fa1d8af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n典型貿易card game，主要出牌攞標記、標記換分數，考腦筋/考策略<br />\n上次同D fd玩，第1鋪就上手，都幾好玩<br />\n5人game (上次我地2個一組)<br />\n<br />\n3) 阿瓦隆<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/154609_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F154609_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=6fb8bf97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相似既狼人game，大家唔知大家係好人定壞人<br />\n壞人要隱藏身份，阻止好人出任務成功<br />\n又係好簡單，玩1-2鋪就上手<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你地聽日安排有咩game<br />\n如果有興趣既可以帶出黎研究下"},{"pid":"fdb1a9cc1954d119b2ee3a532c1f2f60d5690112","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽晚得閒，想知有咩玩？<br />\n洗唔洗我帶D board game黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地好多都係新手，巴打你會有咩介紹？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時我都會買/帶D 新board game同我d fd玩，試過以下幾隻都OK易上手<br />\n<br />\n1)<br />\nBang The Dice Game<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/153550_ed143da556835022bf9220d523aacde8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F153550_ed143da556835022bf9220d523aacde8.jpg&h=a406a16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三國殺初原&quot;Bang&quot;既變化版，<br />\n用骰仔玩，變相隻一次都好靠運氣，所以更加容上手<br />\n<br />\n2) 香料之路<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/154032_ed32cbb9ca71ce300768f88acbd8f348.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F154032_ed32cbb9ca71ce300768f88acbd8f348.png&h=1fa1d8af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n典型貿易card game，主要出牌攞標記、標記換分數，考腦筋/考策略<br />\n上次同D fd玩，第1鋪就上手，都幾好玩<br />\n5人game (上次我地2個一組)<br />\n<br />\n3) 阿瓦隆<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/154609_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F154609_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=6fb8bf97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相似既狼人game，大家唔知大家係好人定壞人<br />\n壞人要隱藏身份，阻止好人出任務成功<br />\n又係好簡單，玩1-2鋪就上手<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你地聽日安排有咩game<br />\n如果有興趣既可以帶出黎研究下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBang 同阿瓦隆 係唔錯<br />\n我地多數因為總會有d 新人，同埋大家都係內向底，我地會玩d 破冰既game 先，等大家熟d warm up d 先，雖然有d 弱智，但係都無辦法。<br />\n多數玩1－2個game，慢慢由開心反應game－－＞有d 智力，同溝通強小小既game，因為我地希望內向朋友可以藉住game 多d 交流，唔想成日玩d 自己一個係咁諗野既game。<br />\n<br />\n我地d game 有d 弱智嫁，上次玩Dixit，猜猜畫畫合家歡，今次諗緊玩德國小強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175532896485bf0c68b105d3819b9cfc33f08a35","tid":309112,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"簡單報告一下今日完左既聚會啦<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位支持，收到唔少巴絲支持，可能太遲開post，大部分人都未能抽時間出席啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，最後都有十個巴絲黎到，總括黎講都開心既。<br />\n原來大家都幾鍾意用腦，下次可以再用多d 腦筋。<br />\n<br />\n下個月會繼續係呢到招募大家，多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940399a2967191764c7fd91a7b5062eb2c1f567d","tid":309112,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}